  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic, ginger, cinnamon, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper to the pot and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the palm sugar and stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer it to the oven, where it will cook at 300°F (150°C) for 2 hours.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and stir in the ghee and cilantro.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
